# Crontabs of Tim on Hexagon run on node1
# To set up cron job on ONE node, a) > ssh login1, > b) crontab timcrontab, c) > exit 
# 1) Check restarts from topaz                           - Every day @1800
# 2) Check wamsea                                        - Every day @1800
# 2) Forecast run                                        - Every day @1900 
# 3) Converting products into .nc files                  - Every day @2100
# 4) Merging the .nc files into one final_product        - Every day @2110
# 5) Archiviation of model's products                    - Every day @2130
#
